# Frontend Architecture Mastery

## Overview

This repository demonstrates advanced frontend architecture patterns through small focused mini-projects.

---

## Projects

1. Feature-Based Architecture  
2. Clean Architecture Refactor  
3. State Orchestration  
4. Performance Architecture (TBD)
5. Design System Architecture (TBD)
6. System Design (TBD)

---

## Goals

- Demonstrate senior-level frontend architecture
- Provide production-grade patterns
- Showcase scalability and maintainability

---

## Tech Stack

- React
- TypeScript
- React Query
- Zustand
- Vite
- Jest / Testing Library
- Playwright

---

## Key Skills

- Architecture design
- State management
- Performance optimization
- UI system design
- Testing strategy

